    "description": "Yuma, a first-year student, shows up for a trial session at his high school's struggling volleyball club. Surprisingly, his preferred position is the bench! Due to a heart condition, he can only exert himself at full power for exactly five minutes. Why did he join the club with such a heavy restriction? In front of the confused members, he unleashes extraordinary, top-tier plays during his brief window. It turns out Yuma was actually a legendary player during his middle school days! A boy who shines brighter than anyone else for a limited time shatters the common sense of sports\n\n**Official Japanese**\n\n[Manga Zegra](https://manga-zegra.com/series/27c5ff3df24ab?utm_source=ig&utm_medium=social&utm_content=link_in_bio&fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnl_SjEqS75ps463ns6xSNzY-XxYTqNcVdYlPSB_Q_wzA6bYNfYombpGgfgT4_aem_y7DuCCZyeXTyOq8U7t4u9Q)\n\n",
